    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> I assume that the long term plan is to get Quorum support in the new migrations framework?\r\n\r\nCurrent plan, not even long-term! We've been making headway on it lately (mostly @CruzMolina), and active work continues as issues like these are identified. It's a priority for us, and I'm sure Cruz is probably about ready by now for the Quorum integration to be done and work as expected ðŸ˜„.\r\n\r\nLast I heard, there was an issue with truffle-hdwallet-provider and Tessera, but that's different than your issue, it seems. Unless they're the same, which would be nice. Apart from that, I believe migrations _should_ work? This is the first I'm hearing of this issue with the deployer, so I'm not sure what you could do to fix it right now, apart from using the old syntax. Hopefully we can just get this fixed for you real fast.",
