    "body": "This has nothing to do with Tessera. \r\n\r\nFor quorum you fall back to legacyMigration code. That is about the same as truffle v4 migration code. \r\n\r\nIn v5 you added the option to have async migrations, but this was not added in the legacy v4 style code. \r\n\r\nBy using the workarounds we used while using v4, everything works (both on quorum and on parity), but nice optimised v5 code that works on parity will not work on quorum.",
